<subSubSection id="C36B652A81E2FF4EFF31F942FEDDF8AB" pageId="205" pageNumber="206" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BCE36A181E2FF4EFF31F942FCD9F8DE" blockId="205.[136,1452,1742,1913]" box="[189,874,1778,1805]" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">
<emphasis id="B905EAB381E2FF4EFF31F942FEC6F8DE" bold="true" box="[189,373,1778,1804]" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">Distribution:—</emphasis>
Northern 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181E2FF4EFE6DF943FDFDF8DF" box="[481,590,1779,1805]" name="Myanmar" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
and southwestern 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181E2FF4EFC93F942FCD5F8DE" box="[799,870,1778,1804]" name="China" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">China</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCE36A181E2FF4EFF31F8A6FEDDF8AB" blockId="205.[136,1452,1742,1913]" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">
<emphasis id="B905EAB381E2FF4EFF31F8A6FE95F8E2" bold="true" box="[189,294,1814,1840]" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">Notes:—</emphasis>
A new record for 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181E2FF4EFE66F8A7FDEAF8E3" box="[490,601,1815,1841]" name="Myanmar" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
. In his revision of the Asian species, Efimov said: “This species is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D2281E2FF4EFF04F88BFEF7F886" box="[136,324,1850,1876]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Platanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="205" pageNumber="206" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nematocaulon">
<emphasis id="B905EAB381E2FF4EFF04F88BFEF7F886" box="[136,324,1850,1876]" italics="true" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">P. nematocaulon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and may be conspecific with it. The main difference is that 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D2281E2FF4EFC62F88BFB70F886" box="[1006,1219,1850,1876]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Platanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="205" pageNumber="206" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="handel-mazzettii">
<emphasis id="B905EAB381E2FF4EFC62F88BFB70F886" box="[1006,1219,1850,1876]" italics="true" pageId="205" pageNumber="206">P. handel-mazzettii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a larger flower” (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B5081E2FF4EFF03F8EEFED2F8AB" author="Efimov, P. G." box="[143,353,1886,1913]" pageId="205" pageNumber="206" pagination="1 - 233" refId="ref222872" refString="https: // doi. org / 10.1134 / S 1234567813030063 Efimov, P. G. (2016) A revision of Platanthera (Orchidaceae; Orchidoideae; Orchideae) in Asia. Phytotaxa 254: 1 - 233." type="journal article" year="2016">Efimov 2016: 154</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
